{"tid":1080612,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人缺乏同理心係好痛苦","createTime":"2019-03-27T17:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T21:14:38.000Z","uid":133963,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c89a5cbf8751ca001d0c19894ac8259c2204a45f","tid":1080612,"uid":133963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人同我一樣<br />\n冇辦法去理解其他人既感情<br />\n唔係冷血 見到窮人訓街既都會心唔舒服<br />\n只係太過自我中心 <br />\n用自己既角度看待事情<br />\n理解唔到人係唔同處境下既感覺<br />\n<br />\n「子非魚，焉知魚之樂」<br />\n<br />\n無法去代入其他人既內心世界<br />\n令到自己無法好好處理各種關係<br />\n讀書讀親歷史同人文學科缺乏一種切身體會<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道點解會咁？"},{"pid":"f406d1022abff432611708f1348e2dfb69bb8afb","tid":1080612,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T20:22:58.000Z","msg":"同成長有關"},{"pid":"afc47ba0736abfa694dfcbb4428ab743c4e97888","tid":1080612,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T20:24:55.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 好似個心死左咁 覺得好多野都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57e839ea8e4166f27a4ad39b84418a7c09054f7","tid":1080612,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T21:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同樣<br />\n但我覺得唔係無同理心，係好快接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}